# Directions to L100 Poison Trainer (Dark Cleric, mob 6788)

say { "Hello";
	say What is it ye seek %n?;
	}

say { "trainer";
	tell %n Finding your next trainer is part of your training.;
	tell %n However, I can give you a hint....;
	tell %n Racial disputes broad and grim,;
	tell %n It's a wonder how much blood is spilled.;
	tell %n Dare not take ye a dwarf within,;
	tell %n Or surely the Elves will pound him!;
	tell %n North of Grimhaven then set your pace east...;
	tell %n there a simple tree will be.;
	}

